 | footnote=施洗者聖約翰縣人口普查数据<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/population/cencounts/la190090.txt|title=Louisiana Population of Counties by Decennial Census: 1900 to 1990|author=美国人口调查局|accessdate=2007-06-12|archive-date=2007-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071231182413/http://www.census.gov/population/cencounts/la190090.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref>
